                              መላእክተ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ አብሰራ፡ ፍሥሐ፡ ወሐሤት፡ ለኵሉ፡ ዓለም፡ ሰባኬ፡ ፀሐይ፡
                              ወፀዋሬ፡ ዜና፡ ብስራት፡ ጥዑም፡ </explicit>
                      </msItem>

                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                          <locus from="13v"/>
                          <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" cert="medium" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3956Homily">
                             በስመ፡ <gap reason="omitted" resp="PRS9602Turaev"/>
                             ድርሳን፡ ዘደረሰ፡ አባ፡ እለ፡ እስክንድሮስ፡ አወፈ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡
                            ዘሀገረ፡ ፈይም፡ </title>
                          <note>The homily for 25 Sane assigned to
                            Alexander ʾAfaw Bishop of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC3066Fayyum">Fayyum</placeName>,
                            on the occasion of
                            the consecration of the church of St
                            Michael in the monastery of ʾAqlon. The author's name is
                            probably confused, otherwise this text is ascribed to
                            Bishop Sawiros of Fayyum.</note>
                      </msItem>
